In: main.go
Out: main.go

ledger.AddTransaction() must not take a transaction number.
generating the transaction number is the responsibility of the ledger.
Ledger must store transactions in a slice; the slice index is the transaction number.

BalanceSheetsAt() must take a transaction number, look up the
transaction by slice index, and return a map of party names to balance sheets.
